A state of child at the age of young
======================================
When one supply enery to themself contineously from long time, they feel their 
heart is melting, thier ego is disapering.
If they try to take revenge from some one their ego not support the pick up sate.
They feel too much emotional, thier thought rotate around feeling.

During melting sate of heart due to contenious supply of enery one 
obserb their behavious/feeling/thought..etc and one realize it is in state of change.

***It all about feeling when a young person realize/observe his own behaviour like child***.

One can realize their mom is most beautifl on the earth. How much one get feeling from thier mom
that much feeling not get form any others humans.

One can realize thier youngness behavious is slightly disapearing. One try to become serious but their feeling
not support to become the same.

One heart too much with small event also and one heal much with small event also.
 If some one scold you, at the place of respond you just get hearted.
At this state one not tens but heart much.

you always fumble your nature/behaviour. It is diffcult to tell anyone what you realize 
but realization of kidness always with you.

***A state of child at the young age is a state on the path of meditation***

When you are with your emotion at this sate.
-------------------
If you look serious to some one you cant stop your laugh. You realize why any one 
is in state of serious.
You break the serious metting by your smile. It may be possible to laugh to see some one in tense.
you can observe the intial state of energy in some one from where they start to become serious.

When you are oppoite to your emotion at this state
-------------------
You feel heart like child. This is highly painful. You suffer lot by your own feeling.
You heart like you are a child and your mom is going away from you for a long time.

***From this state you can observe how much child heart but unable to respond back when one harm them***
